name: Dynamic Active Energy Evolution ETF
longDescription: DXET seeks to provide long-term capital appreciation and income primarily through investment in a diversified portfolio of companies involved in renewable energy or related activities from around the globe. In seeking to achieve its investment objectives, DXET intends to invest primarily in equity securities of companies involved in renewable energy or related activities, with no geographic constraint.
